/*/ Insert your company colors below,
The first four assets are the buttons in the course,
For the ".__active" assets, reverse your colors (this is for when buttons are pressed)/*/

.btn.btn-muted {background-color: white; color: black; border: 1px solid black;}
.btn.btn-muted.__active {background-color: black; color: white; border: 1px solid black;}
.btn.btn-solid {background-color: white; color: black; border: 1px solid black;}
.btn.btn-solid.__active {background-color: black; color: white; border: 1px solid black;}

